CodeDef mailto Filter
CodeDef mailto Description mailto: link
CodeDef mailto Routine <<EOR
sub {
	my ($val,$tag,@arg) = @_;
	my $out = qq{<a href="mailto:$val">};
	my $anchor = $val;
	if(@arg) {
		$anchor = join " ", @arg;
	}
	$out .= "$anchor</a>";
}
EOR
